{"tid":998260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有無道理？】叫學生校內勿說中文 美大學學者捱轟辭職","createTime":"2019-01-27T23:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T08:50:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b7f3c82e49b35b0d80ccf158722f935c9484a7","tid":998260,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:26:08.000Z","msg":"【有無道理？】叫學生校內勿說中文 美大學學者捱轟辭職<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%BE%8E%E6%9D%9C%E5%85%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%B6%89%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%BF%E8%AA%AA%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-159561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%259D%259C%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258B%25BF%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587-159561&d=au7646NPa1FOxU9yFhTa9b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=bb4609ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%BE%8E%E6%9D%9C%E5%85%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%B6%89%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%BF%E8%AA%AA%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-159561</a><br />\n<br />\n美國杜克大學(Duke University)生物統計系碩士課程主管尼利(Megan Neely)，前日向課程的一、二年級學生發出電郵，指有兩名教職員分別向她報告，稱有學生在學校範圍「非常大聲地說中文」，要求查看學生相片，找出說中文的學生後記錄他們的名字，在日後申請實習的面試或畢業項目時可認得他們，又指那些學生沒有善用改善英語的機會，並用一種在校內不是任何人都聽得懂的語言溝通很不禮貌，尼利希望國際學生謹記在校內無意中說中文可帶來的後果，鼓勵「在100％的時間內使用英語」。該電郵的截圖被上載到社交網後引來大量批評，指涉種族歧視，該校醫學院院長遂向學生致歉，而尼利亦辭去其職務。"},{"pid":"7631403b17eed77370c6318ed4f5b6d1182a1aee","tid":998260,"uid":117679,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港啲貴族學校好似有校規講明上學時唔講得中文。咁呢啲係唔係要抄家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2e9adb14d11c9778690f9bdfb1a10edae3a81d","tid":998260,"uid":190714,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:33:49.000Z","msg":"有幾唔禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb25857554c74728eaf2eaf96863a7193c2b4ad8","tid":998260,"uid":29297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:35:22.000Z","msg":"蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e6d2fb25c8232b3e2a5300a3e3c997529a2e76","tid":998260,"uid":208159,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:43:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0ab980ff869195ca8767860812b3998a1064faa","tid":998260,"uid":166474,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:46:05.000Z","msg":"支那人去到邊都累街坊，咁鍾意講蝗語唔番支那讀大學？"},{"pid":"8467740da9bc556a62f8805c13b5c09e70cc453e","tid":998260,"uid":96704,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:48:37.000Z","msg":"如果唔係係咩professional既場合大家用返母語溝通都唔係問題掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過大大聲咁講就唔係幾好咁囉"},{"pid":"523c6d249a56fdb9b08c8dc8fa3b1b0aaf8c73d9","tid":998260,"uid":127611,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:49:48.000Z","msg":"公道講句<br />\n自己圍內講，又唔係同你講<br />\n你就要點人相搞人實習同畢業<br />\n咁做法好撚唔公平姐"},{"pid":"dd1ba75807cdd63967ac3f625988260d28aa8448","tid":998260,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RanK4We.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRanK4We.png&h=e60931b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuNfr9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuNfr9z.png&h=adf429ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ffd92fcdbf481b0aa93e87050ede1d5b5ae3da0","tid":998260,"uid":130401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:02:13.000Z","msg":"咁係學校個陣 屋企人打黎 佢唔識英文都要用英文講野<img src=\"/as